{"tid":1444134,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"「和理非朋友請幫忙置頂」可罷用/罷買嘅化妝護膚品牌","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T12:48:55.000Z","uid":260766,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"978abfc8322cd5c56251e132ec6e0197fdaf7166","tid":1444134,"uid":260766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:33:10.000Z","msg":"同朋友吹水，佢之前有巴打話杯葛某堆tvb嘅化護膚品牌，但發現大家搞錯咗d品牌同替代品牌，所以佢叫我同大家講清楚可以杯咩同用咩品牌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9Fg1Yp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9Fg1Yp.jpg&h=8d723ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇清楚嗰表就知L字頭集團有咩品牌，大家諗諗可以點做。<br />\n<br />\n(L 字頭公司品牌) -&gt; (替代品牌)<br />\n<br />\nLancome -&gt; Estee Lauder, SKII (呢個牌子就自己諗諗，會推薦EL 多d), Clarins (莊思敏&hellip;&hellip;), Sulwhasoo (搵咗陳凱琳做promote)<br />\n<br />\nGiorgio Armani Beaute/ YSL -&gt; Clau de Peau Beaute, Chanel Beaute, Dior Beaute<br />\n<br />\nUrban Decay -&gt; MAC, NARS <br />\n<br />\nShu Uemura -&gt; MAC, Bobbi Brown<br />\n<br />\nMaybelline-&gt; Revlon, Kate,  Etude House, Benefit, 3ce<br />\n<br />\nNYX-&gt; Too Faced, Kiko Milano<br />\n<br />\nBiotherm -&gt; Laneige, Origins<br />\n<br />\nHelena Rubinstein-&gt; La mer , La Prarie <br />\n<br />\nRoger &amp; Gallet -&gt; Sabon, Loccitane <br />\n<br />\nLoreal Paris-&gt; Neutrogena, Olay (Olay就自己諗諗佢)<br />\n<br />\nKiehl's -&gt; Fresh, Clinique<br />\n<br />\nAtelier Cologne -&gt; Jo Malone, Chanel, Dior, Diptyque, Byredo, Tom Ford <br />\n<br />\nLa Roche Posay -&gt; Bioderma, Avene<br />\n<br />\nVichy -&gt; Clinique, Bicelle<br />\n<br />\nSkin Ceuticals -&gt; Bicelle, Obagi<br />\n<br />\nCerave -&gt; Cetaphil, Aveeno<br />\n<br />\nKeratase -&gt; Aveda, Moroccanoil<br />\n<br />\nLoreal Brand list:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.loreal.sg/brand\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loreal.sg%2Fbrand&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqnljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=cca18923\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.loreal.sg/brand</a> <br />\n<br />\n簡單一句，唔買Loreal, 可睇LVMH, Sofina 同 Amore Pacific 旗下嘅Brands <br />\n<br />\n係噤多先，我冇嘢講。"},{"pid":"63b63bfaeab1567ec7d19ee88fc0895f9ead6124","tid":1444134,"uid":34908,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:11:02.000Z","msg":"有樣要補充 3ce賣左俾loreal<br />\n<br />\n其他絲打都整理得好好<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d114502dac94a50f5017b04d75a5e02f00c19cff","tid":1444134,"uid":260766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63b63bfaeab1567ec7d19ee88fc0895f9ead6124","tid":1444134,"uid":34908,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:11:02.000Z","msg":"有樣要補充 3ce賣左俾loreal<br />\n<br />\n其他絲打都整理得好好<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:18:09.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打。sor, 仲有it cosmetics 都係Loreal 嘅，幫忙推推佢。thx"},{"pid":"609abaef01ead020e8f44f7bda29e96168e71249","tid":1444134,"uid":17746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ce8c459940f1a3d341a38a5d6a44f77c2547fd69","tid":1444134,"uid":47819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貼去化妝post吧樓主,有2個<br />\n仲有香水，gel甲，等等女人post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af32f4ca3b5ee63ccd208d8bc481e6c0f04b129a","tid":1444134,"uid":12920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:38:04.000Z","msg":"其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經罷買左L&rsquo;Or&eacute;al group 好耐"},{"pid":"f3265f35863f8bac94542e3b1eb232f724f283c4","tid":1444134,"uid":162373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa